in file TextHelper.php, function excerpt_text()
    Extracts an excerpt from the +text+ surrounding the +phrase+ with a number of characters on each side determined by +radius+. If the phrase isn't found, nil is returned. Ex: excerpt("hello my world", "my", 3) => "...lo my wo..." If +excerpt_space+ is true the text will only be truncated on whitespace, never inbetween words.
